## Suggested Improvements

### 1. 🛡️ Add Input Parsing Middleware with Size Limits
Without body-parsing middleware (and size limits), the app is vulnerable to large payload attacks if you add POST/PUT routes later.

```js
app.use(express.json({ limit: '10kb' }));
app.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: false, limit: '10kb' }));
