| No security headers | 🔴 High | Add `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | 🔴 High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No global error handler | 🔴 High | Add `(err, req, res, next)` middleware |
| No 404 handler | 🟡 Medium | Add catch-all route |
| No payload size limit | 🟡 Medium | Add `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| Hardcoded port | 🟡 Medium | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| PII exposure in `/users` | 🟡 Medium | Whitelist response fields |
| No input validation | 🟡 Medium | Validate all route params/query strings |

